node.text:
1212 Gateway launching December 12th!! I can’t believe I’m actually saying that now! I spent the past couple of years devoting myself to this project and it’s finally here. I started this in a past life and never got to finish it...✨
I know you guys will love it as much as I do!

Let your soul glow.

MOTHER OF THE SEA🌊

Coming soon ✨🧜‍♀️ @1212gateway
